(78,0,'creature_ai_scripts','event_inverse_phase_mask','Mask for the event.','This field allows to restrict the event occurences to certain EventAI phases. The EventAI script phases are changed with actions 22 and 23, see below. This mask contains 1 in the bits corresponding to the phases for which you DO NOT wish the event occuring.<br />The default value 0 means that the event may happen in any script phase. The value 1 will disable the event for the phase 0 while keeping it enabled for all other phases. The value 5 will disable the event for phases 0 and 2, and so on.'),
